To use the program type: 
<input file path> <output file path> <filter name> [additional parameter]

Available filters:
grey 
median
gauss
sobel

Additional parameter is required if you want to apply gauss filter or sobel filter.
If you choose gauss you have to put either 3 (if it is 3x3 gauss filter) or 5 (the case of 5x5 filter).
In case you want to apply the sobel filter type x , y or xy

Example: /home/username/Documents/bird.bmp /home/username/Documents/result.bmp sobel xy
